Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:33.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:38.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:43.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:48.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:08.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:33.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:43.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:33.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寬恕促人前行 仇恨讓人停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:38.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:43.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒讓你一直停滯不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:48.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名為永不凋謝之花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也無法永不凋謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:08.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}認真活著就會有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此斷言的話語必定是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之幾十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之幾不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:33.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:43.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原諒你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くコノ手デ掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戻っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして今　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が分からなくてもいい　そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境なく燃える炎を　雲中が指を指す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと　強くなって　誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したい人の思い　闇をコノ手デ祓おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣 我追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親手去緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 則無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到原點也一樣 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無法保護珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 我會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無人知曉也無妨 只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃盡萬物的烈焰 直衝雲霄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要變強 保護所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心懷所愛之人 親手驅散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔劍居然是明陀宗的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父親還和明陀有過接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快點接著唸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我開始有種不好的預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然不知道勝呂的老爸想讓我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男 總之你先繼續唸信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡就是明陀宗以前的據點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔堂就在這裡面 我們抓緊時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是 那裡真的安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這座不動峰寺以降魔堂為中心 就是為了守護它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}右眼原來應該是封印在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}物歸原處才是上策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久沒爬過這座山了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}七 八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 你們這些猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她來了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能接近這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在這裡呀 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父親很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡就是降魔堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡只有座主能進入 是不可侵犯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家一定不會原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是現在座主和本尊都不在了 這裡只剩一個空殼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}護摩壇竟然還生著火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡肯定有暗道 找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在證明住持大人 勝呂達摩能夠信任之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:59.01,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,1022)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(356,605)}綿裡藏針
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被奉為明王陀羅尼宗的本尊 代代相傳的魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又名俱利伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相傳 明陀始祖不角用此劍召喚了火之惡魔伽樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用它的火之力打倒了不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從那以來 明陀宗代代將此劍奉為本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了封印殘留的右眼 讓它遠離俗世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}定下了嚴格的戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像是在嘲諷這一切一般 他出現在了我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你在說什麼 那把劍是明陀的本尊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真囉嗦 我知道 禿驢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反正這裡頭也是空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說些什麼莫名其妙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別碰我們的本尊 你個賊人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打倒他了嗎 八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不愧是八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他早就受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傷得這麼重 虧他還能動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這人怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩大人 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正十字騎士團日本支部 上一級驅魔師 藤本獅郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}金剛深山不動峰寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你突然倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不能就那樣把你丟著不管 就把你搬到寺廟裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把我丟在那兒不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是個老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能借個火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起這種事 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}關於本尊 關於俱利伽羅 你知道多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你為什麼想要俱利伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎麼知道 上級叫我來的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大概是要用它殺小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}殺小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他居然滿不在乎地說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身體能動了你就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管你有什麼原因 我可不照顧一個殺小孩的惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會走的 等我拿到降魔劍之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你還不放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你都不知道它在這不動峰寺的何處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要把每間屋子都找一遍不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 沒那麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是問你更快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 劍在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什麼 想用它和我打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那裡是… 不能去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}閉嘴 別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混蛋 你知道你在做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是不和佛祖對話 佛祖就會放棄我們 我們就會失去力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我問你 只是祈禱就能救這些人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}披著聖人外衣的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最討厭你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經不是做這種事的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必須盡快將瘴氣的毒素排出體外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他 他們還能得救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能 他們所有人都能得救 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去準備白蘿蔔 蔥 纈草 菖蒲 岩鹽 還有朝天椒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有凡士林 蜂蠟 豬油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們真的有救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要我說幾遍啊 你去準備大量的熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}點煙的火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果他真的 真的救了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的以為自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的能生下這孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你來搶劍的時候 我還以為你是什麼山賊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我誤會你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這和那是兩碼事 把劍交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我救了那麼多病人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還教了你們治療的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我點回禮也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎 虎子你先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還以為你是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是我最討厭的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不問你了 我自己去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}害怕被玷污是無法前進的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 婀蜜哩帝 吽 癹吒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他逃了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能讓那賊人活著走出這座山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 你在做什麼啊 他可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩 別以為這次我會輕易饒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼正十字騎士團的驅魔師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不僅讓邪教之徒進入了寺院 還讓他去蠱惑人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 他是我們的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他救了大家 救了虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種事怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了降魔劍和明陀秘密的外人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能斬盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有責任守護明陀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你守護的只是戒律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩 你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 真纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}害得我傷口都裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我告訴你逃走的路線 跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想幹什麼 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事 其實我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我小時候偷偷把劍拔出來過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想看一看伽樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}結果伽樓羅和火焰都沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那把劍只是個空殼 我一直都知道 卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不想再膜拜一把空殼劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我終於也下定決心 決定去戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是要用它去殺小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 你一定不會殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是個無可救藥的濫好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}腳印往那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你快逃 這樣我們就兩清了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣我們就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 他跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在下面 我們繞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤本和我的故事就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幾個月之後 青之夜就發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父親將座主之位以及明陀真正的秘密傳給我 然後去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個秘密真的十分可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藏在這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到降魔堂裡竟然有這樣的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把右眼給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但拿著兩個會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就快到了 而且我更擔心你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有點後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只因為我的推測 就將我重要的學生捲進了這麼不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想想你的今後 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在能保護大家的只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我們打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安政五年 你們的祖先不角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曾與附有火之惡魔伽樓羅的魔劍「俱利伽羅」結下契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們雖拚盡全力與不淨王戰鬥 卻未能將其斬殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能取其雙目 將不淨王封印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那之後 伽樓羅離開了俱利伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是明陀宗傳說的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是你們明陀宗代代守護的最深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個是不淨王？ 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這150年間一直在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那右眼和左眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 只要將右眼和左眼還給乾涸的不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能讓不淨王完全復活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老師 你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是我重要的學生 雖然我也不忍心說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但你已經沒有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會帶你回到你父親那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是會危害人類的毒瘤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必須在我這一代將其消滅 決不能留到下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由我來保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有礙此決意者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明陀宗第十七代座主勝呂達摩決不饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那青色的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我繼承了明陀宗座主之位 知道了所有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.90,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 你能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.68,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別死啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾名為伽樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乃明王陀羅尼座主之使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汝乃先祖不角之子孫否
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向吾示以血緣之證
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我是勝呂達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不角的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}確有不角之血緣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂達摩 吾今後將聽命於汝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道代代座主都可以使役伽樓羅嗎 這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要什麼作為交換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾之所求乃秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾之存在 吾為何聽命於汝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一切真相皆為秘密 須死守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是代價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:16:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾實則生於秘密 以謊言與猜忌之塵芥為食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作為交換 吾將予汝封敵之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敵人是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沉睡於此佛堂地下余150年之殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽樓羅啊 就是現在 給我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}契約就是如此 我會答應你的所有請求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又叫朱雀或者不死鳥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是個不錯的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然不知道你有何企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我絕不會讓你輕易復活不淨王的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放下右眼和左眼 退散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我這幾年就是為了這個瞬間而活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽樓羅焰 火食之印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身體能力好強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被惡魔附體之人大都如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽樓羅焰 火粉之印
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恢 恢復速度跟不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是伽樓羅的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼就讓我使出絕招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王要復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔堂 他來這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人 蝮也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是柔造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 小心那些飛沫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是八百造叫你來的吧 真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先不要管這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你能幫忙把蝮帶到外派所 去叫增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個怪物到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但她把不淨王的右眼放到身體裡受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你替我將她帶回她父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在這裡阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要告訴大家真相 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們走 蝮 抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的秘密暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}與明陀宗座主的契約就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有和我個人定下的另一個契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不淨王開始成長並擴散瘴氣之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少要使出淨火封之印來拖住它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使用淨火封之印要消耗大量的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使用劫波焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劫波焰是你為了打倒不淨王而練
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若是現在使用 你將永遠失去打倒不淨王的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曩謨三滿多母馱喃 阿缽囉底賀多 舍娑曩喃 哈諾迦諾迦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}佉佉 佉呬佉呬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劫波焰 淨火封之印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 暫時讓它停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這 這可真是費勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我都警告過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還沒死 只要活著就能找到打倒牠的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做了很對不住寶生同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為你太神秘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不會輕易出現在人前 也不知道你在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想了很久要怎樣將你引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能想到復活不淨王了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我早就知道明陀宗靠伽樓羅之力來封印不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但為了這一天 還是費了我好幾年的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的目標是你 勝呂達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 確切來說是你的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他把伽樓羅吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超出想像的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}強行讓伽樓羅附在了自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人類干涉惡魔 怎麼會有這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感覺年輕不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是伽樓羅的力量附帶的好處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它在我肚子裡亂竄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看來我這個容器還沒法完全控制住它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過 總會適應的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣離我的目的又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你了 勝呂達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託你了 奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能用降魔劍打倒不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道這是個無理又勉強的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果 如果你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像你父親那樣對我施以些許慈悲之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想將希望寄託於你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你看到最後 勝呂達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:05.38,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第七集 氣焰萬丈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 把劍還回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的火焰對到目前為止遇到的惡魔都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一試
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請打倒不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}經三賢者以下的審問委員會投票決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}處決奧村燐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老頭子 為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
